																										<div class="thumb-wrap"><img width="600" height="370" src="https://thaipbs-world.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/thaipbsworld/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/25174716/AP21137559604242-600x370.jpg" class="attachment-medium size-medium wp-post-image" alt="" srcset="https://thaipbs-world.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/thaipbsworld/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/25174716/AP21137559604242-600x370.jpg 600w, https://thaipbs-world.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/thaipbsworld/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/25174716/AP21137559604242-768x473.jpg 768w, https://thaipbs-world.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/thaipbsworld/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/25174716/AP21137559604242-1024x631.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" /></div>																									</div>									
												<div class="post-content">
